'''Owas Ray Mwape''', ni umukinnyi [[Zambiya|wa]] firime wa [[Zambiya]], umukinnyi wumwanditsi.  Umukinnyi wa firime ufite ubuhanga bukomeye, Mwape yatangiye umwuga we nkumukinnyi kandi azwi cyane mubikorwa bya '''''Mwansa the Great'', ''[[:en:Suwi|Suwi]]'' and ''Fever''''' 

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavukiye i Ndola . Yabanje gushyingiranwa n'umukinnyi w'indirimbo uzwi cyane wo muri [[Zambiya]], Saboi Imboela.  Nyuma baje gutandukana aho Imboela yerekanye ihohoterwa rikorerwa mu ngo rya Owas.  Icyakora, nyuma Owas yahakanye ibirego n'ibihuha bitari byo kuri we na Imboela. 

== Umwuga ==
Mwape yatsindiye ibihembo byigihugu byumukinnyi witwaye neza mumyaka itatu ikurikiranye ya 1990, 1991 na 1992, abaye umunyaZambiya wenyine wageze kuriyi ntsinzi kugeza ubu. Yatangiye gukina bwa mbere kuri filimi ''Kabanana'' kuva 2004 kugeza 2008. Nyuma yaje gukina filime nyinshi hamwe na serial nka ''The Lawyer'', ''Redbag'', ''Complicated Affairs'', ''Justice at Stake'', ''The Wife'', ''Mwansa the Great'', ''Chidongo'', ''The ticket'', ''A beautiful Lie'' and ''Guilt''.. Muri 2013, yashinze isosiyete ye bwite itunganya filimi 'Owas Films' maze ahindukira akora amashusho yigihe cyose. Muri 2015, yayoboye filime ebyiri ''Chenda'' na ''Secrets Untold'' aho iyi ifite premier yayo muri Ster Kinekor i Lusaka. 

